{"article_id":"guBb9ggsJUFcgJr8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LISTEN TO ARTICLE 3:03","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"SHARE THIS ARTICLE","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Share Tweet Post Email","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Terms of Trade is a daily newsletter","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that untangles a world","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"embroiled in trade wars .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Sign up here .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"China and the U.S. agreed on the text of a phase one trade deal","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that includes the removal of tariffs on Chinese goods in stages ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Vice Commerce Minister Wang Shouwen said ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"as President Donald Trump confirmed","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that some levies will be reduced","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"the next round of talks will start immediately .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"China will increase imports from the U.S. and other countries ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Wang said at a briefing in Beijing Friday .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Vice Chairman of the National Reform and Development Commission Ning Jizhe added","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that the specifics of agricultural purchases would be released later ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"as the text of the agreement is still under review .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The comments were China ' s first response to a deal","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"signed off by Trump on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that would halt higher tariffs","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"planned for Dec. 15","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and represent the first phase","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"in defusing the trade war","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that ' s shaken the global economy .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" we have agreed to a very large Phase One Deal with China .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"They have agreed to many structural changes and massive purchases of Agricultural Product , Energy , and Manufactured Goods , plus much more .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The 25 % Tariffs will remain as is ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"with 7 1/2 % put on much of the remainder ... \" We have agreed to a very large Phase One Deal with China .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"They have agreed to many structural changes and massive purchases of Agricultural Product , Energy , and Manufactured Goods , plus much more .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The 25 % Tariffs will remain as is ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"with 7 1/2 % put on much of the remainder ....","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"December 13 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"By keeping much of the existing tariffs in place ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Trump told reporters later Friday","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that the U.S. would have leverage in the next round of talks .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"\" We ' ll use them for future negotiations on the phase-two deal , \"","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that his administration was planning to wait until after the 2020 election for the next step .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"\" They ' d like to start them sooner than that ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and that ' s OK . \" ..... The Penalty Tariffs","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"set for December 15th","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"will not be charged","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"because of the fact","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that we made the deal .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"We will begin negotiations on the Phase Two Deal immediately ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"rather than waiting until after the 2020 Election .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"This is an amazing deal for all .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Thank you !","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"December 13 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"U.S. stocks initially rallied ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"with the S & P 500 Index jumping to a record ,","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"but were little changed after the announcements .","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"The world ' s two largest economies have been in a trade war for about 18 months","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"involving nearly $ 500 billion in products","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"shipped between the two nations .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"The deal text ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"which comprises nine chapters ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"includes sections on intellectual property , forced technology transfer , food and agricultural products , finance , currency and transparency , boosting trade , bilateral assessment and dispute resolution ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"according to Chinese officials .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Both sides agreed to finish the final stages such as legal review and translation as soon as possible","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"and work on arrangements for the final signing ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"said Wang .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"First announced by Trump on Oct. 11 ,","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"the interim deal with China offers a short-term political victory for the president","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"and will allow him to claim","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that his tariffs have paid dividends ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"at the risk","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"of being accused of postponing tougher issues like China ' s industrial subsidies .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Unfolding along with the trade news on Friday was the House Judiciary Committee ' s recommendation","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"to impeach Trump .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"Read More :","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Trump Impeachment Advances","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"as Historic Vote Sends Case to House","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"For Beijing , reducing even some of the tariffs","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that have been imposed since last year","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"represents a win for President Xi Jinping ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"who is also facing pressure","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"to not give in to the other side .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"\" Without doubt ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to implement the agreement ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"our imports of American agricultural goods will increase significantly , \"","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Vice Agriculture Minister Han Jun said .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Trump told reporters","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Chinese purchases of agricultural goods would hit $ 50 billion \" pretty soon . \"","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"- With assistance by Lucille Liu , Miao Han , Sharon Chen , James Mayger , Josh Wingrove , and Katia Dmitrieva","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":100,"right":186,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":99,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":95,"right":98,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":3,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":152,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":118,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":111,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":106,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":102,"right":105,"relation":"context","nucl